{"version": 2, "width": 100, "height": 30, "timestamp": 1784437202, "idle_time_limit": 2.0, "env": {"SHELL": "/bin/bash", "TERM": "xterm-256color"}, "title": "Gorilla — settlement engine, one engine settled by proof"}
[0.005211, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.807054, "o", "\u001b[1m\u001b[35mGORILLA — SETTLEMENT ENGINE\u001b[0m  \u001b[2mone engine, settled by proof\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[2.010407, "o", "\r\n"]
[2.81385, "o", "\u001b[2mTwo different products settle through ONE shared engine:\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[3.617402, "o", "\u001b[2m  · a betting market  \u001b[0m(who won?)\r\n"]
[4.421229, "o", "\u001b[2m  · an insurance policy  \u001b[0m(did the thing happen?)\r\n"]
[5.224864, "o", "\u001b[2mNeither re-checks the proof itself. Neither can skip the safety —\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[6.028342, "o", "\u001b[2mthe engine binds every result to its exact game, stat and period.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[7.430959, "o", "\r\n"]
[8.23395, "o", "\u001b[36m$ cargo test -p forge-markets-tests\u001b[0m\r\n"]
